    "Overall_Summary": {
      "Call_Synopsis": "The customer called regarding an exchange of a 6-month-old Queen mattress (from another brand) for a Duroflex King mattress. The agent correctly informed the customer that external exchanges are not possible but successfully pivoted by offering disposal assistance and inviting the customer to the store to avail year-end offers on a new King mattress.",
